* The comparison is case sensitive.
* </p>
*
* <pre>
* StringUtils.equals(null, null)   = true
* StringUtils.equals(null, "abc")  = false
* StringUtils.equals("abc", null)  = false
* StringUtils.equals("abc", "abc") = true
